description: Sweetbites is the vision of founder Sandra Panetta, an environmental scientist with a finely calibrated sweet tooth. Born into an Italian family, she learned from childhood how to bake European-style desserts, and soon brought her own unique flair to her ancestors’ recipes. After years of experimentation, Sandra launched her own catering business in 2001 specializing in exquisite pastries, cupcakes and tarts. Her gourmet cupcakes are found in DC’s finest neighborhoods and have earned a loyal following among customers at the Broad Branch Market in DC, and Sweet Leaf in McLean, VA.
name: sweetbites
